author: COMSOL
description: This example studies the stationary state of free convection in a cavity filled with air and bounded by two vertical plates. To generate the buoyancy flow, the plates are heated at different temperatures, set in a range to keep the regime laminar. The simulation is run in 2D and 3D geometries.
